description:
*Christianity: Hollywood's Favorite Joke* | In this age of heightened sensitivity and cancel culture, everyone is encouraged to be extra careful to not "offend" anyone. Meanwhile, Hollywood has no problem slamming Christianity or God—and hardly anyone makes a fuss. Isn't it ironic that it's acceptable to mock God, yet the world so readily labels it as a hate crime when Christians speak up about things that the Bible defines as sin?
